&lt;Derlan Industries Ltd> said it plans toissue 2.1 mln common shares in a private placement at a priceof 14 dlrs per share for gross proceeds of 29.4 mln dlrs.    The issue will be placed by McLeod Young Weir Ltd andLoewen, Ondaatje, McCutcheon and Co Ltd.    Proceeds will be used by the company to continue itsacquisition program and for internal expansion. Reuter&#3;